      "description": "Available is a 2003 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather. At its heart is the S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This example features the desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a fresh mechanical refresh, including a comprehensive dual-VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement\u2014critical preventative measures for this chassis. The suspension has been enhanced with Koni Yellow adjustable dampers and Powerflex polyurethane bushings for sharpened turn-in and reduced lateral deflection. While the exterior shows minor stone chips and light wear indicative of its mileage, the drivetrain remains exceptionally tight with no fluid leaks or oil consumption. This is a mechanically sound, driver-spec M3 ready for the canyons.",
